OL,3,CMan, 36, shot dead in broad daylight
OL,4,Cnamed
OL,6,FThe family of a man shot dead on
OL,7,FMerseyside have released a photograph
OL,8,Fof him.
OL,10,F36-year-old Rikki Berry, known locally
OL,11,Fas 'Nuggy', was shot outside a house
OL,12,Fon Quarryside Drive in Kirkby shortly
OL,13,Fafter 6.30pm on Wednesday 17 July.
OL,15,FOfficers attended the scene and he was
OL,16,Ftaken to hospital by paramedics where
OL,17,Fhe was pronounced dead a short time
OL,18,Flater.
OL,20,FHis family are being supported by
OL,21,Fspecialist family liaison officers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
