OL,4,Cnamed
OL,6,FMerseyside Police has confirmed a 20-
OL,7,Fyear-old from Kirkby has been arrested
OL,8,Fon suspicion of murder and remains in
OL,9,Fcustody.
OL,11,FDetective Chief Inspector Cath
OL,12,FCummings, the senior investigating
OL,13,Fofficer, said: "The arrest of this man
OL,14,Fis just one part of this process and
OL,15,Fthe extent of his involvement will
OL,16,Fform part of our enquiries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
