OL,3,CMan, 36, shot dead in broad daylight
OL,4,Cnamed
OL,6,F"I want to emphasise that this
OL,7,Finvestigation is in its very early
OL,8,Fstages and extensive work is underway
OL,9,Fto find anyone who may have been
OL,10,Finvolved.
OL,12,F"It initially appears to have been a
OL,13,Ftargeted shooting, carried out in
OL,14,Fbroad daylight in view of witnesses,
OL,15,Fwho will have understandably been left
OL,16,Fshocked and upset at what happened.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
