OL,3,CMan, 36, shot dead in broad daylight
OL,4,Cnamed
OL,6,F"If you live in the area, please check
OL,7,Fyour CCTV, dashcam devices or doorbell
OL,8,Ffootage urgently around this time and
OL,9,Fpass on anything which may assist.
OL,10,FHowever small a detail you may think
OL,11,Fyou hold, let us make the
OL,12,Fassessment...Our thoughts and
OL,13,Fcondolences remain with Rikki's
OL,14,Ffamily, who will now be supported by
OL,15,Fspecialist officers as the
OL,16,Finvestigation progresses."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
