OL,3,CMan, 36, shot dead in broad daylight
OL,4,Cnamed
OL,6,FKnowsley Local Policing Superintendent
OL,7,FKarl Baldwin said: "The Kirkby
OL,8,Fcommunity will see a lot of activity
OL,9,Fin the area today and I want to
OL,10,Fencourage people to speak to our
OL,11,Fofficers.
OL,13,F"We understand that people are
OL,14,Fsometimes reluctant to speak to
OL,15,Fpolice, but be assured that we will
OL,16,Fdeal with information sensitively and
OL,17,Fput necessary measures in place to
OL,18,Fsupport those who help, as well as
OL,19,Fproviding highly visible policing in
OL,20,Fthe area in the coming days.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
