OL,3,CMan, 36, shot dead in broad daylight
OL,4,Cnamed
OL,6,F"We will have a mobile police station
OL,7,Fin the Northwood area in the next
OL,8,Fweek, so please speak to us. Gun crime
OL,9,Fcauses devastation, as last night's
OL,10,Ftragic events sadly show. We will do
OL,11,Fall we can to bring those responsible
OL,12,Fto justice, and remove weapons from
OL,13,Fthose communities who suffer from the
OL,14,Fgreat harm that organised crime
OL,15,Fbrings."
